{"tid":498301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第三圈投選專區(171214)","createTime":"2017-12-13T15:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T05:09:01.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0554df301d682db960d017bbaf8ba908f69ffa1","tid":498301,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(超)謝安琪vs陳法拉(冠)<br />\n(非)陳靜vs簡淑兒(超)<br />\n(甲)劉穎鏇vs簡幗儀(冠)<br />\n(超)李靜儀@SGvs杜小喬(超)<br />\n(超)倪晨曦vs陳嘉倩(超)<br />\n(超)林嘉欣vs鄧麗欣(冠)<br />\n(超)麥明詩vs馮盈盈(超)<br />\n(超)李佳芯vs陳瀅(超)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36965ac6d989e525dd8a94b231c16fc78af95542","tid":498301,"uid":92376,"like":25,"dislike":27,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第三圈</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-14 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rsj1853.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Frsj1853.png&h=ddc72cec&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a09GUCK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa09GUCK.png&h=423467c8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: cen